name: WhyTheLongFace #01
description: Welcome to the Basilius. The ‘why the long face’ is inspired by the famous Joker comment in the comic book ” A horse walks into a bar . The bartender asks,” why the long face?”. We wanted the NFT Community to have a little fun and enjoy our collection. This collection has 10k unique NFT’s selected from a million auto-generated NFT’s of which 5000 will be here on opensea and another 5000 will be on Rarible. We are uploading every day until we upload all 10000 of them on both sites. Thank you for checking our NFTs and have a Great day.
